TAKING APPLICATIONS FOR AUGUST 1ST MOVE-INS!<br>
<br>
Schedule your in person tour for this large and spacious 1 bedroom 1 bath apartment home ready for you today!<br>
<br>
Are you working from home and in need of space? This one bedroom features a huge walk in closet in the bedroom, plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen plus an amazing view from your balcony. We welcome you to stop by and take advantage of this great apartment home.<br>
<br>
