WILL NEED WHEN APPLYING<br>
<br>
<br>
A government issued ID<br>
A Copy of your Social Security Card<br>
An application for everyone moving in over the age of 18<br>
An application fee of $40.00<br>
A Holding deposit of $200.00. If approved this amount will go towards your security deposit.<br>
Security deposit starts at $1000 on approval of good credit and references.<br>
We do conduct income, rental, background and credit checks.<br>
We require, as a household, that the income be at least 2 ½ times the rent. (Verifiable income)<br>
<br>
Cashier's Checks or Money Orders Only<br>
PET POLICY<br>
Must be under 25 pounds<br>
2 pets per household<br>
$45 (per pet) pet rent<br>
