DESCRIPTION<br>
Welcome to Evergreen Ridge Apartments. Our apartments offer an enviable location near great shopping and delicious local restaurants just minutes away from your doorstep. If you feel like going for a bike ride or jog, wonderful trails are located nearby for your enjoyment! The surroundings at Evergreen live up to the community’s name, with idyllically kept trees and a charming courtyard. Here at Evergreen Ridge Apartments, we are dedicated to ensuring your comfort. Our attentive staff is here to ensure your home is always in excellent shape, and we respond quickly to maintenance needs when they arise. We offer a selection of one and two bedroom homes within the community ensuring that you find the perfect combination of floor plan and features. If you are ready to make Evergreen Ridge Apartment homes your next home. Choose your new home today!<br>
